n<br />\n\tSelection refers to the process of choosing. What is the selection? How is it determined? What will be the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They made their selection... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) food selection<br />\n\t2) selection process<br />\n\t3) a wide selection available<br />\n\t4) natural selection<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWhile walking towards the club office, the manager seemed to be in a good mood, and he was making small talk with the interior designer. Since going through a few sketches should not take too long, that was why Hodge insisted that the interior designer stayed for a meal at the club after the meeting. Other than drinks and appetizers, there was also quite a broad range of food selection at the club. Even if the interior designer might not have known this, he still politely accepted the dinner offer.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169826351832/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p869654/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p869654\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p835818/\">双语美文：珍惜当下，因为失去总是猝不及防</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p726432/\">英语四级听力提分攻略</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p895566/\">Quora精选：歪果仁喜欢哪些中国产品？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p895515/\">口语必备：怎样提高英语发音？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.h